0.17 2026-06-20
  - Ticket history: the per-transaction action icons (toggle-contrast, reply,
    comment) are now vertically centered on the metadata bar instead of sitting
    ~8px below the date/subject line. Core history.css floats the (taller) icon
    box out of the flow; the redesign now lays the metadata bar out as a flex row
    so the icons align on the baseline. Applies to every message and comment row.

0.16 2026-06-19
  - Admin dashboards (Admin, Global, CustomFields, Articles, Assets, Tools) now
    show a "last update" timestamp for the cached statistics, below the stat
    cards, via the shared /Elements/StatsRefreshedNote
  - Timestamp timezone: the login page shows the RT server timezone ($Timezone,
    normally UTC); the admin dashboards show the logged-in user's own timezone
    preference
  - New helper RT::Extension::Redesign::format_refreshed_at() (uses RT::Date for
    timezone handling); the login page now uses it too (removes the duplicated
    strftime formatting)
  - Note text changed from "Statistics updated twice daily. Last update: X" to
    "Last update: X" (the refresh frequency is cron-configurable, not fixed);
    all 37 translations updated accordingly. Admin note is right-aligned.

0.15 2026-06-19
  - FeedWidget: SSRF guard — FetchFeed now refuses feed hosts that resolve into
    private, loopback or link-local ranges (10/8, 127/8, 169.254/16, 172.16/12,
    192.168/16, ::1, fe80::/10, fc00::/7, IPv4-mapped); an authenticated user can
    no longer use the server-side fetch to probe the internal network
  - FeedWidget: bumped to 1.0.1

0.14 2026-06-19
  - Makefile.PL: perl floor now derived from `use 5.010001;` in the main module via
    all_from(); removed redundant author() (was duplicating the META author)
  - Makefile.PL: removed install_script() — RTx already ships bin/ into the plugin
    dir; install_script routed the script to /usr/local/bin and broke `make install`
  - META.yml: regenerated by Module::Install (was a stale ExtUtils::MakeMaker copy
    with license: gpl); now license: gpl_2, single author, perl: 5.10.1, x_requires_rt
  - MANIFEST: dropped inc/Module/Install/Scripts.pm (no longer bundled without
    install_script)
  - .gitignore: ignore the POD-generated plain-text README (only README.md tracked)

0.13 2026-06-19
  - Redesign.pm: Groups SQL made portable via $dbh->quote_identifier (no literal backticks)
  - AboutThisUser callback hardened

0.12 2026-06-18
  - Aligned META.yml version with the module

0.11 2026-06-18
  - Tests kept local only; dropped t/ from MANIFEST

0.10 2026-06-12
  - Redesign.pm: MySQL 8 fix — all queries against Groups table now use rt3.Groups prefix
  - Redesign.pm: collect_stats() now wrapped in section-level eval blocks; errors
    logged via RT::Logger, partial results returned instead of dying
  - Redesign.pm: new admin section in collect_stats() for Admin/index.html stats
    (queues, CFs, users, tickets by status)
  - All Admin pages: removed per-process <%once> cache; pages now read stats from
    the AdminDashboardStats RT::Attribute (populated by rt-redesign-stats-refresh)
  - All Admin pages: DB queries retained as fallback when attribute not yet populated

0.08 2026-06-09
